(1)

\[ f_{\theta_1,\theta_2}(x,y)={1 \over 2\pi\sigma_{\theta_1}\sigma_{\theta_2}\sqrt{1-\rho^2}}e^{{-1\over 2(1-\rho^2)}[({x-\mu_{\theta_1} \over \sigma_{\theta_1}})^2-2\rho({x-\mu_{\theta_1} \over \sigma_{\theta_1}})({y-\mu_{\theta_2} \over \sigma_{\theta_2}})+({y-\mu_{\theta_2} \over \sigma_{\theta_2}})^2]} \] \[ where ~ \mu_{\theta_1}=0.3 ~~ \mu_{\theta_2}=0.58 ~~ \sigma_{\theta_1}=\sqrt{1/30} ~~ \sigma_{\theta_2}=\sqrt{1/30} ~~ \rho=0.5 \]

library(mvtnorm)

x <- seq(0.3-0.5,0.3+0.5,0.01)
y <- seq(0.58-0.5,0.58+0.5,0.01)
sig=matrix(c(1,0.5,0.5,1),nrow = 2)/30

f <- function(x,y){dmvnorm(cbind(x,y),c(0.3,0.58),sig)}

contour(x,y,outer(x,y,f))

\[ f_{\theta_1} (x)={1\over\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma_{\theta_1}}e^{-{1\over2}{(x-\mu_{\theta_1})^2\over\sigma_{\theta_1}^2}}~~~~~~where~\mu_{\theta_1}=0.3,~ \sigma_{\theta_1}=\sqrt{1/30} \]

plot(x,dnorm(x,0.3,sqrt(1/30)),type = 'l')

\[ f_{\theta_2}(y)={1\over\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma_{\theta_2}}e^{-{1\over2}{(y-\mu_{\theta_2})^2\over\sigma_{\theta_2}^2}}~~~~~~where~\mu_{\theta_2}=0.58,~ \sigma_{\theta_2}=\sqrt{1/30} \]

plot(y,dnorm(y,0.58,sqrt(1/30)),type = 'l')

(2)

\[ f_{\theta_2|\theta_1}(y|x) = \frac{1}{{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma_{\theta_2|\theta_1}^2}}} \exp\left(-\frac{{(y - \mu_{\theta_2|\theta_1})^2}}{{2\sigma_{\theta_2|\theta_1}^2}}\right) \] \[ \mu_{\theta_2|\theta_1} = \mu_{\theta_2} + \rho \frac{{\sigma_{\theta_2}}}{{\sigma_{\theta_1}}} (\theta_1^{(0)} - \mu_{\theta_1}) = 0.58+0.5*{\sqrt{1/30}\over\sqrt{1/30}}(0-0.3) = 0.58-0.15 = 0.43 \\ \sigma_{\theta_2|\theta_1}^2 = (1 - \rho^2) \sigma_{\theta_2}^2 = (1-0.5^2){1\over30} = 0.75/30 \]

\[ f_{\theta_1|\theta_2}(y|x) = \frac{1}{{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma_{\theta_1|\theta_2}^2}}} \exp\left(-\frac{{(y - \mu_{\theta_1|\theta_2})^2}}{{2\sigma_{\theta_1|\theta_2}^2}}\right) \] \[ \mu_{\theta_1|\theta_2} = \mu_{\theta_1} + \rho \frac{{\sigma_{\theta_1}}}{{\sigma_{\theta_2}}} (\theta_2^{(0)} - \mu_{\theta_2}) = 0.3+0.5*{\sqrt{1/30}\over\sqrt{1/30}}(0-0.58) = 0.3-0.29 = 0.01 \\ \sigma_{\theta_1|\theta_2}^2 = (1 - \rho^2) \sigma_{\theta_1}^2 = (1-0.5^2){1\over30} = 0.75/30 \]

(3)

M=3000 ; m=500
xbar=0.3 ; ybar=0.58
sig1=sqrt(1/30) ; sig2=sqrt(1/30) ; rho=0.5

THETA=matrix(nrow=M, ncol=2)

#initial value
mu1=0 ; mu2=0

for(i in 1:M){
  condpost.theta1=xbar+rho*sig1/sig2*(mu2-ybar)
  condpost.var1=(1-rho^2)*sig1^2
  mu1=rnorm(1,condpost.theta1,sqrt(condpost.var1))
  
  condpost.theta2=ybar+rho*sig2/sig1*(mu1-xbar)
  condpost.var2=(1-rho^2)*sig2^2
  mu2=rnorm(1,condpost.theta2,sqrt(condpost.var2))
  
  THETA[i,]=c(mu1,mu2)
}

THETA=THETA[m:M,]

# theta1 사후 기대치, 사후 분산
mean(THETA[,1])
## [1] 0.2975366
var(THETA[,1])
## [1] 0.03326387
# theta2 사후 기대치, 사후 분산
mean(THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.5781514
var(THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.0345444
# 상관계수
cor(THETA[,1], THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.4971202

(4)

plot(THETA[,1],THETA[,2])

plot(density(THETA[,1]))

plot(density(THETA[,2]))

거의 같은 결과를 같는다.

Q2

(1)

\[ f_{\theta_1,\theta_2}(x,y)={1 \over 2\pi\sigma_{\theta_1}\sigma_{\theta_2}\sqrt{1-\rho^2}}e^{{-1\over 2(1-\rho^2)}[({x-\mu_{\theta_1} \over \sigma_{\theta_1}})^2-2\rho({x-\mu_{\theta_1} \over \sigma_{\theta_1}})({y-\mu_{\theta_2} \over \sigma_{\theta_2}})+({y-\mu_{\theta_2} \over \sigma_{\theta_2}})^2]}I(\theta_1<\theta_2) \] 주변 사후밀도함수식은 수리적으로 구할 수 없다. ## (2) \[ f_{\theta_2|\theta_1}(y|x) = \frac{1}{{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma_{\theta_2|\theta_1}^2}}} \exp\left(-\frac{{(y - \mu_{\theta_2|\theta_1})^2}}{{2\sigma_{\theta_2|\theta_1}^2}}\right)I(\theta_1<\theta_2) \]

\[ f_{\theta_1|\theta_2}(y|x) = \frac{1}{{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma_{\theta_1|\theta_2}^2}}} \exp\left(-\frac{{(y - \mu_{\theta_1|\theta_2})^2}}{{2\sigma_{\theta_1|\theta_2}^2}}\right)I(\theta_1<\theta_2) \] ## (3)

M=3000 ; m=500
xbar=0.3 ; ybar=0.58
sig1=sqrt(1/30) ; sig2=sqrt(1/30) ; rho=0.5

THETA=matrix(nrow=M, ncol=2)

#initial value
mu1=0 ; mu2=0

for(i in 1:M){
  condpost.theta1=xbar+rho*sig1/sig2*(mu2-ybar)
  condpost.var1=(1-rho^2)*sig1^2
  mu1=rnorm(1,condpost.theta1,sqrt(condpost.var1))
  if(mu1>=mu2){
    mu1=0
  }
  
  condpost.theta2=ybar+rho*sig2/sig1*(mu1-xbar)
  condpost.var2=(1-rho^2)*sig2^2
  mu2=rnorm(1,condpost.theta2,sqrt(condpost.var2))
  if(mu1>=mu2){
    mu2=0
  }
  
  
  THETA[i,]=c(mu1,mu2)
}

THETA=THETA[m:M,]

THETA <- THETA[THETA[,1] != 0 | THETA[,2] != 0,]

THETA <- THETA[THETA[,1]!=0,]
THETA <- THETA[THETA[,2]!=0,]

# theta1 사후 기대치, 사후 분산
mean(THETA[,1])
## [1] 0.2557665
var(THETA[,1])
## [1] 0.03455337
# theta2 사후 기대치, 사후 분산
mean(THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.5785185
var(THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.03313697
# 상관계수
cor(THETA[,1], THETA[,2])
## [1] 0.5955212

(4)

plot(THETA[,1],THETA[,2])

plot(density(THETA[,1]))

plot(density(THETA[,2]))
